__**General Rules**__
1. Keep the chat and posts relevant to the channel
2. Please treat everyone in the server with **respect**. **No racism, hate, or harassment**
3. No politics
4. No drama
5. No doxxing / other illegal activities
6. No spreading misinformation
7. No spam/flooding the chats
8. No trolls, no impersonations
9. No NSFW or ecchi (Both media and text)
10. English please
11. Please refrain from using rude/lewd names or profile pictures**\***
12. Follow the Discord Guidelines/ToS


Please also check the channel descriptions for channel-specific rules!

**\***(If you dont want to change your username you can ask the Mods to set a Nickname for you.)
